  <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
    <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
      <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">What's in the App?</strong>
      This is a Rails 6 (PostgreSQL) example todo and blog application that utilizes React, Coffeescript, jQuery &amp; Bootstrap to shape the frontend.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
    <%= image_tag 'tayberry.svg', class: 'mr-2 rounded' %>
    <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
      <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">Lorem</strong>
      Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
    <%= image_tag 'schnozberry.svg', class: 'mr-2 rounded' %>
    <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
      <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">Lorem Ipsum</strong>
      Donec id elit non mi porta gravida y barranco at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh <a href="https://github.com/TonyMaseda/rails-react-bootstrap" target="_blank">enlacita</a>, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.
    </p>
  </div>
  <small class="d-block text-right mt-3">
    <%= link_to('Sign in', new_user_session_path) %> or <%= link_to("Sign up", new_user_registration_path) %>
